40
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:27,960
Speaker 0: And we are going to be doing, sadly, they didn't want us to do any of our new panels, so you'll have to wait until, I guess, the New York Anime Festival, or maybe, maybe, Connecticut to see Tales from the Anime Club.

41
00:02:28,701 --> 00:02:31,771
