1446
01:13:59,135 --> 01:14:02,240
Speaker 0: This con we only did like we did three panels.

1447
01:14:02,360 --> 01:14:05,205
Speaker 0: And then like the anime squares, we just kind of we were guests on it.

1448
01:14:05,265 --> 01:14:06,587
Speaker 0: That was the same as doing a panel.

1449
01:14:07,368 --> 01:14:12,597
Speaker 0: Got to spend a lot of time hanging out with people and going to panels and doing all the stuff that I like doing.

1450
01:14:12,617 --> 01:14:14,320
Speaker 0: The reason I used to go to anime cons.

1451
01:14:14,600 --> 01:14:15,421
Speaker 1: Yeah, it's sort of weird.

1452
01:14:15,461 --> 01:14:28,200
Speaker 1: It's like I thought that, you know, because I had been to so many anime cons that like there was no more excitement in dealers rooms or artists alleys or panels because I had seen so many and been to so many that I was just like, well, if I'm not doing I'm not having fun.

1453
01:14:28,280 --> 01:14:36,289
Speaker 1: The thing was right, is that at these conventions, I was having fun when I was doing panels and I wasn't having fun when I wasn't doing them.

1454
01:14:36,649 --> 01:14:41,715
Speaker 1: because I didn't I wasn't really actually able to do anything because I wasn't doing the panel last year.

1455
01:14:41,775 --> 01:14:46,740
