Speaker 0: Thing is, a ton of people came to that panel and they loved it.

1462
01:15:04,085 --> 01:15:04,325
Speaker 0: Yeah.

1463
01:15:04,666 --> 01:15:15,920
Speaker 1: But yeah, so actually doing stuff at the con, you know, and especially because there were so many people there that we sort of knew, you know, that we didn't get to see very often, you know, convention friends, Boston friends.

1464
01:15:16,540 --> 01:15:16,741
Speaker 0: Yep.

1465
01:15:16,921 --> 01:15:17,903
Speaker 0: We hung out with Kat.

1466
01:15:17,943 --> 01:15:19,025
Speaker 0: She was that artist's alley table.

1467
01:15:19,045 --> 01:15:20,167
Speaker 0: We didn't get to hang out with her more.

1468
01:15:20,709 --> 01:15:24,095
Speaker 0: And like we were going to go to dinner with some people, but we lost like half the group.

1469
01:15:24,155 --> 01:15:26,380
Speaker 0: So we didn't actually get to eat dinner with Vega and all them.

1470
01:15:26,680 --> 01:15:33,600
