1471
01:15:34,001 --> 01:15:34,221
Speaker 0: Yep.

1472
01:15:34,922 --> 01:15:41,692
Speaker 0: But Anime Boston kind of, I realized to strike the balance, we're in all cons from now on.

1473
01:15:41,893 --> 01:15:46,540
Speaker 0: Fewer, more focused panels and nothing else other than hanging out and having fun.

1474
01:15:47,443 --> 01:15:47,623
