1478
01:15:52,444 --> 01:15:53,447
Speaker 0: It was last year.

1479
01:15:53,467 --> 01:15:55,273
Speaker 0: We walked in Saturday morning.

1480
01:15:55,293 --> 01:15:57,220
Speaker 0: We did panel, panel, panel and we left.

1481
01:15:57,721 --> 01:15:58,061
Speaker 1: Yeah.

1482
01:15:58,822 --> 01:15:59,063
Speaker 1: Wow.

1483
01:15:59,964 --> 01:16:07,334
Speaker 1: You know, I mean, New York Anime Festival is a little different because it's mostly is just a big room without a lot of, you know, stuff.

1484
01:16:07,394 --> 01:16:09,658
Speaker 1: But I mean, we didn't see anyone else's panels or anything.

1485
01:16:09,698 --> 01:16:11,300
Speaker 1: And it was probably something to see.

1486
01:16:11,540 --> 01:16:12,122
