1487
01:16:12,182 --> 01:16:20,540
Speaker 0: But my love of anime cons is rekindled and I'm looking forward to Otacon more than I've looked forward to any Otacon in years.

1488
01:16:21,281 --> 01:16:25,852
Speaker 0: Just because, one, we're only doing three panels and it's the same three stupid panels.

1489
01:16:26,013 --> 01:16:28,800
Speaker 0: I don't have to do crap except rewrite the Know Your Creators panel.

1490
01:16:29,560 --> 01:16:29,641
Speaker 1: Yeah.

1491
01:16:29,661 --> 01:16:31,172
Speaker 1: I think we're going to turn it into a clip panel, right?

1492
01:16:31,313 --> 01:16:32,260
